Important Information:

Public Open Days: Third Sunday of the Month from 11 AM – 3 PM

Location: 5202 Zoo Drive Los Angeles, CA 90027 (in Griffith Park)

Tickets: Reservations are required for Sunday, July 21. No reservations are required for Sunday, August 18 and the dates going forward.

For Latest Updates: Follow @WaltsBarn on Instagram or Twitter
